coulomb charge moving at 1 meter

00:02:44.827 --> 00:02:48.241
per second,
perpendicular to the magnetic

00:02:48.241 --> 00:02:51.816
field B of 1 tesla,
it will experience a force of 1

00:02:51.816 --> 00:02:52.280
Newton.
 

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:53.180
That's it.
 

00:02:53.180 --> 00:02:58.188
