00:07:25.790 --> 00:07:27.990
B is this way,
perpendicular.

00:07:27.990 --> 00:07:31.420
Take the cross product,
you will get the same force.

00:07:31.420 --> 00:07:34.269
In other words,
the force on the curved segment

00:07:34.269 --> 00:07:37.740
between two points is the same
as the force on a straight

00:07:37.740 --> 00:07:39.910
segment joining the two points.
 

00:07:39.910 --> 00:07:43.160
This happens to be universally
true in a uniform field.

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:46.456
In other words,
even if the wire did this,

00:07:46.456 --> 00:07:49.110
don't bother to find the force.
 

00:07:49.110 --> 00:07:53.540
It's just simply the force on
