so basically the point I'm

00:12:56.441 --> 00:13:00.113
making is,
this loop would like to have

00:13:00.113 --> 00:13:03.889
its area vector parallel to the
magnetic field.

00:13:03.889 --> 00:13:05.820
That's what you've got to
understand.

00:13:05.820 --> 00:13:09.423
It will align itself so that
the most amount of magnetic

00:13:09.423 --> 00:13:11.259
