00:23:13.464 --> 00:23:16.710
so at any instant,
every place looks the same.

00:23:16.710 --> 00:23:20.086
So a steady current is what
we're talking about,

00:23:20.086 --> 00:23:22.960
not a charge going at steady
velocity.

