00:28:34.430 --> 00:28:35.619
Student: 
&gt;

00:28:35.619 --> 00:28:36.269
Prof: That's right.
 

00:28:36.269 --> 00:28:41.950
Take a tiny line segment,
dl, here.

00:28:41.950 --> 00:28:44.348
Join at that point,
