00:29:27.630 --> 00:29:30.019
There's an element dl,
if you want,

00:29:30.019 --> 00:29:32.118
coming out of the blackboard
here.

00:29:32.118 --> 00:29:36.180
And the separation vector is
this one.

00:29:36.180 --> 00:29:40.088
If you take the cross product
of that vector with that vector,

00:29:40.088 --> 00:29:41.868
you've got to think about where
it will be,

00:29:41.868 --> 00:29:45.118
and it's got to be
perpendicular to this vector,

00:29:45.118 --> 00:29:47.250
therefore in the plane of the
