00:29:47.250 --> 00:29:48.818
And it's got to be
perpendicular to this vector.

00:29:48.818 --> 00:29:53.974
And if you do your signs right,
it will give you magnetic

00:29:53.974 --> 00:29:58.210
contribution dB that
