00:53:33.811 --> 00:53:36.380
has length r times
dΦ.

00:53:36.380 --> 00:53:39.371
r is this one,
and points in the direction of

00:53:39.371 --> 00:53:41.659
the unit vector in the phi
direction.

00:53:41.659 --> 00:53:44.518
So
e_Φ

00:53:44.518 --> 00:53:46.860
is unit vector like that.
 

00:53:46.860 --> 00:53:50.579
