00:54:27.219 --> 00:54:30.847
In other words,
I want that distance to be

00:54:30.847 --> 00:54:32.440
little r.
 

00:54:32.440 --> 00:54:33.409
You can also use big R.
 

00:54:33.409 --> 00:54:35.981
It's going to cancel out,
but I'm not taking a fixed

00:54:35.981 --> 00:54:36.889
